      "amount": "1-2 tablespoons"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F (190°C).",
    "Finely chop the tomatoes, onion, garlic, and finely dice the thyme.",
    "In a large pan, heat olive oil over medium heat. Add onions and garlic; sauté until softened.",
    "Add crushed tomatoes, mustard, salt, and chopped tomatoes to the pan. Stir well, reduce for 20 minutes or until mixture thickens.",
    "Transfer sauce into a baking dish. Sprinkle with crumbled tofu or tempeh (for a dairy-free option) and bake at 375°F (190°C) for 20-25 minutes or until golden brown."
